    (Ôłâ k, ¤ć k) Ôćĺ (Ôłâ m, ¤ć m Ôłž ÔłÇ n < m, ┬Č ¤ć n) := by
  intro ÔčĘk, h_kÔčę
  induction k using Nat.strong_induction_on
  case h k IH =>
    cases k
    case zero =>
      use 0
      constructor
      ┬Ě exact h_k
      ┬Ě simp
    case succ k =>
      by_cases ¤ć k
